long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Download and export your order history from eBay, TCGplayer, Card Kingdom and more. OrderWand downloads all of your Magic the Gathering, Pokemon, Flesh and Blood orders to your web browser and allows you to export it to CSV (Excel/Google Sheets/etc) and JSON. 

Home page: http://orderwand.com/

Help: http://orderwand.com/help/
Privacy policy: http://orderwand.com/privacy/
Blog: http://orderwand.com/blog/
